data.name: GetCustomerSalesRevenueReport
data.value: SELECT CO.customer_id, P.person_first_name, P.person_last_name, SUM(COD.price_with_discount) FROM customer_orders CO LEFT JOIN customer_order_details AS COD ON CO.customer_order_id=COD.customer_order_id LEFT JOIN shop_products SP ON COD.product_id=SP.product_id LEFT JOIN persons AS P ON CO.customer_id=P.person_id WHERE CO.customer_id IS NOT NULL GROUP BY CO.customer_id, P.person_first_name, P.person_last_name ORDER BY SUM(COD.price_with_discount) DESC;

data.name: GetFullProductReport
data.value: SELECT p.product_id, t.product_title, t.product_category_id, m.manufacturer_name, p.unit_price, c.category_name FROM shop_products AS p INNER JOIN product_titles AS t ON t.product_title_id = p.product_title_id INNER JOIN product_manufacturers AS m ON m.manufacturer_id = p.product_manufacturer_id INNER JOIN product_categories AS c ON c.category_id = t.product_category_id ORDER BY t.product_title

data.name: GetProductCategoryReport
data.value: SELECT category_id, category_name FROM product_categories ORDER BY category_name

data.name: GetProductReport
data.value: SELECT p.product_id, t.product_title, m.manufacturer_name, p.unit_price FROM shop_products AS p INNER JOIN product_titles AS t ON t.product_title_id = p.product_title_id INNER JOIN product_manufacturers AS m ON m.manufacturer_id = p.product_manufacturer_id ORDER BY t.product_title DESC

data.name: GetProductTitleSalesRevenueReport
data.value: SELECT /*SP.product_id,*/ PT.product_title,SUM(CO.price_with_discount),SUM(CO.product_amount) FROM customer_order_details AS CO LEFT JOIN shop_products SP ON CO.product_id=SP.product_id LEFT JOIN product_titles PT ON SP.product_title_id=PT.product_title_id GROUP BY /*SP.product_id,*/PT.product_title ORDER BY SUM(CO.price_with_discount) DESC;
